{"tid":1670423,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疑似三毛不斷無限放大「加泰左膠舉共產黨旗」去抹黑加泰人支持共產主義","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T12:34:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":43,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"97c10a9399d007e64e4396adfb009cc2fcfdbb0c","tid":1670423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"會員：Miami #110123<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670385/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670385/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n會員：我一直關注事件 #176282<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670272/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670272/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地係加泰左膠：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/vGKcF3t.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係香港都有「社會主義行動」咁解囉, 只係極少數ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你將一少撮非主流既人去無限放大, 帶風向, 係乜嘢居心? 你係咪HK01？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170109/s00046/f8dcd60bf999b734832ad2a8a3946fc5.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i1.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1619385_446866478773887_1096852778_n.jpg?w=720\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加泰人支持共產主義？<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞係西班牙最富有既地區，係西班牙既香港嚟架！"},{"pid":"113078a4ccbf555972afc1b983a52ea5b4b473f6","tid":1670423,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"三毛空群而出, 又有可能係HK01帶風向<br />\n4個月經驗明證冷氣軍師係ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上港豬天生的怯懦<br />\n<br />\n自己諗啦！"},{"pid":"1b97483ea99f5c62ea71471bd6407272f421d6db","tid":1670423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"又多一隻三毛, 瘋狂散佈抹黑：<br />\n<br />\n無知無我 #208086<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670421/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670421/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4d0b82c44913e8a94116e5544371369239c75bdd","tid":1670423,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=e415cc58\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=70fd3020\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=41f01f29\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=2bee7c4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"86543c73ee76bd9d9de797c24aa5575a781c58ef","tid":1670423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91718f830f52bb2ec952ab710d41cbe14e3c629","tid":1670423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"休息師之後, 又到三毛HK01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a896d881ea5aec0a0725335de859ccf9cc35e4d2","tid":1670423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"黃之峰都出聲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670